# Tournament Tool (Smogon OP & Replay BBCode generator)

## Deploy
1. Push this repository to GitHub.
2. Import it into Vercel (https://vercel.com) and deploy.

## Endpoints (UI uses these)
- GET  /api/test
- GET  /api/parse-thread?url=<SMOGON_THREAD_URL>
- POST /api/detect-tiers  { text }
- POST /api/generate-key  { parsed, options }
- POST /api/generate-replays { parsed, raw, options }

Use the web UI at the root (/) to paste a thread URL and generate BBCode headers & replays.
